summary: A house in Solitude between Hall of the dead and Market Place.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#00ff00][size=5][b]
House in Solitude

[/b][/size][/color][size=3]A Player House near Market Place in Solitude.
Two single beds and a double bed. 
Chest and a big weapon rack.
Books and more...
[b][color=#ffff00]
You can find near Hall of the dead.[/color][/b][/size]
